{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"afabeddaa7","title":"“国家的选举制度不民主”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"14f92fa19e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"afabeddaa7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"167ba6e3e1","name":"傅锟"},{"id":"2625b3be8b","name":"袁传炽"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"ba91c1b3de","name":"姚洪烈"},{"id":"cd6d1d2c70","name":"李燕吉"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5117842b77","type":"title","text":"“国家的选举制度不民主”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7"},{"id":"9f8c4c86cc","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院袁传炽李燕吉姚洪烈傅锟","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7"},{"id":"c106fc6cc7","type":"paragraph","text":"袁传炽说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7"},{"id":"e3588f547d","type":"paragraph","text":"「国家的选举制度也不民主，名单都决定了，才叫人选。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7"},{"id":"720ea4b109","type":"paragraph","text":"李燕吉说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7"},{"id":"257c356c02","type":"paragraph","text":"「选举制度由中共和民主党派协商提名单后再选不应该，应该象资本主义国家那样。」","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7"},{"id":"6db4c06452","type":"paragraph","text":"姚洪烈说：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7"},{"id":"c301474608","type":"paragraph","text":"「协商提名后，你不选，大家还是选他，如果自由竞选，民主党派也不一定选不上。」","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7"},{"id":"755147668f","type":"paragraph","text":"傅锟说：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7"},{"id":"a043ec2204","type":"paragraph","text":"「我们不妨要社会主义民主内容，而采取资产阶级民主形式，解放前，有些作法很民主，如选学生会执委，可以出墙报，互相宣传，这种形式是好的，现在的内容是民主的，形式还不够，如人民代表选举等，是否可以竞选一下？」","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7"}],"page":{"id":"19e1863f08","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afabeddaa7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}